      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine and transmission are solid, providing a reliable driving experience, and the interior is clean with only minor signs of use. While the exterior paint still looks great, there are a few small stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular driving. It\u2019s a dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate major repairs.",
